{{!
  Emits the `, returns_initial_response=True` FunctionEntry argument for an
  interaction factory that returns an initial response in request/response form
  (`Interaction, Response factory()`). Gated to non-stream, non-sink: a
  stream/sink factory's leading tuple is its (first_response, stream|sink) pair,
  not a (tile, response) pair, so it must keep the zero-arg `create<Interaction>`
  Tile path rather than the initial-response install path. Invoke with the
  function set as the current context (inside a #function section).
}}
{{#pragma ignore-newlines}}
{{#if (and function:returns_tuple? (not function:stream?) (not function:sink?))}}
, returns_initial_response=True
{{/if (and function:returns_tuple? (not function:stream?) (not function:sink?))}}
